===Noun===
'''command'''  (''plural:'' '''[[commands]]''')
# An [[order]], a compelling task given to an inferior or a machine.
# Unit of [[military]] personnel.
# {{baseball}} The degree of control a [[pitcher]] has over his pitches.
#: ''He's got good '''command''' tonight.''

